# 🚀 GATER.NG – FULL APP DESCRIPTION

## 🧾 Product Overview

**Gater.ng** is a self-service event ticketing and access management platform that enables individuals and organizations to create, promote, sell, and manage event tickets digitally.

It provides an end-to-end system covering:

* Event creation
* Ticket sales
* Payment processing
* Digital ticket issuance (QR-based)
* Event check-in & validation
* Sales and attendee analytics

---

## 🎯 Mission

To make event ticketing in Nigeria **fast, accessible, and reliable**, while helping organizers maximize attendance and revenue.

---

## 👥 Target Users

### 1. Event Organizers

* Churches
* Tech bootcamps
* Concert hosts
* Conference planners
* Training providers

### 2. Attendees

* Individuals looking to discover and attend events

---

## 💡 Core Value Proposition

### For Organizers:

* Launch an event in minutes
* Accept payments instantly
* Eliminate manual tracking
* Prevent ticket fraud with QR validation

### For Attendees:

* Seamless ticket purchase
* Instant digital ticket delivery
* Hassle-free event entry

---

## 🧠 Product Positioning

👉 “The fastest way to create, sell, and manage event tickets in Nigeria.”

---

# 📘 FEATURE DOCUMENT (DETAILED)

---

## 🧩 1. AUTHENTICATION & USER MANAGEMENT

### Features:

* User registration (email/password)
* Login / logout
* Password reset
* Role system:

  * Attendee
  * Organizer
  * Admin

### Optional:

* Google login
* OTP verification

---

## 📅 2. EVENT MANAGEMENT

### Features:

* Create event
* Edit event
* Publish / unpublish event
* Delete event

### Event Fields:

* Title
* Description
* Banner image
* Location (physical or virtual)
* Date & time
* Organizer profile

---

## 🎟 3. TICKET MANAGEMENT

### Features:

* Create multiple ticket types per event:

  * Regular
  * VIP
  * Early Bird
* Set:

  * Price
  * Quantity
  * Sales start/end date

### Capabilities:

* Free tickets
* Paid tickets
* Limited inventory

---

## 💳 4. PAYMENT SYSTEM

### Features:

* Secure checkout
* Payment processing via **Paystack**

### Supported Methods:

* Card
* Bank transfer
* USSD

### System Capabilities:

* Payment initialization
* Payment verification
* Webhook handling
* Failed payment recovery

---

## 🧾 5. ORDER MANAGEMENT

### Features:

* Create order on checkout
* Track order status:

  * Pending
  * Paid
  * Failed

### Data captured:

* Buyer info
* Ticket type
* Quantity
* Payment reference

---

## 🎫 6. DIGITAL TICKETING SYSTEM

### Features:

* Unique ticket ID generation
* QR code generation per ticket
* Ticket validation logic

### Ticket includes:

* Event details
* Ticket type
* QR code
* Attendee name

---

## 📩 7. TICKET DELIVERY SYSTEM

### Features:

* Email ticket delivery
* Downloadable ticket

### Optional (HIGH IMPACT):

* WhatsApp delivery
* SMS notification

---

## 📲 8. EVENT CHECK-IN SYSTEM

### Features:

* QR code scanning interface (mobile-friendly)
* Real-time validation

### Validation outcomes:

* Valid ticket → allow entry
* Already used → reject
* Invalid → reject

### Additional:

* Manual check-in fallback

---

## 📊 9. ORGANIZER DASHBOARD

### Features:

* Event overview
* Ticket sales tracking
* Revenue analytics
* Attendee list

### Data points:

* Total tickets sold
* Total revenue
* Remaining tickets

### Actions:

* Export attendee list (CSV)
* Monitor ticket performance

---

## 🌐 10. PUBLIC EVENT DISCOVERY

### Features:

* Browse events
* Search events
* Filter by:

  * Date
  * Location
  * Category (future)

### Event Page Includes:

* Event details
* Ticket options
* Purchase button

---

## 🛠 11. ADMIN PANEL (INTERNAL)

### Features:

* View all users
* View all events
* Monitor transactions
* Manage disputes
* Issue refunds

---

## 🔐 12. SECURITY & FRAUD PREVENTION

### Features:

* Unique QR per ticket
* One-time check-in validation
* Payment verification via webhook

---

## ⚙️ 13. SYSTEM NOTIFICATIONS

### Triggers:

* Ticket purchase success
* Event reminders (optional)
* Payment failure

---

## 📦 14. FILE & MEDIA MANAGEMENT

### Features:

* Upload event banners
* Store and serve images efficiently

---

## 📈 15. ANALYTICS (BASIC)

### Organizer Insights:

* Sales trends
* Ticket performance
* Attendance rate (after event)

---

# 🔄 CORE SYSTEM FLOWS (SUMMARY)

---

## 🎯 Event Creation Flow

* Organizer signs up → creates event → adds tickets → publishes → shares link

---

## 🎯 Ticket Purchase Flow

* User visits event → selects ticket → pays → receives QR ticket

---

## 🎯 Check-in Flow

* Organizer scans QR → system validates → marks ticket used

---

## 🎯 Organizer Monitoring Flow

* Organizer logs in → views dashboard → tracks sales & attendees

---

